title: Red - End of Silence (Deluxe Edition) [2007]
description:
Deriving from a variety of influences such as Muse, Chevelle, Blindside and Linkin Park, Red brings a unique blend of heavy guitars, intense string arrangements and dynamic vocals. The songs on their debut release "End of Silence" deal with the struggles that all humans face, while leading listeners to a place of redemption in the midst of the brokenness.
[Source: Amazon.com]
